<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA15">
<l>tirintatu veñcamattut tērkaṭavi yaṉṟu</l>
<l>pirintatu cītaiyaimāṉ piṉpōyp – purintatuvuṅ</l>
<l>kaṇpaḷḷi koḷḷa vaḻakiyatē nākattiṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṇpaḷḷi koḷvāṉ ṟaṉakku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That he wandered, urging the chariot in hot battle, that day,</l>
<l>that he separated from Sītā, going after the deer , and that he</l>
<l>to have a bed on the ground  – is that [so] beautiful[ly done] by the one</l>
<l>who has [his] cool bed on the snake?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
